name: ParadiSeat_Facesitting
description:
I mean, it's pretty self-explanatory.

As usual (i need to stop doing that), this is a WIP! I gathered quite the dataset (4K images!) that i intend to manually prune and tag in the future to allow much more flexibility, like 2 girls on a man with one being penetrated, yuri facesitting, and different angles, but do not expect that fancy stuff with this version.

trigger word : "sitting on face". Weight is fine at 0.8, feel free to experiment with it if you try to combine other loras tho.

Background will be boring if you don't write one in your prompt.

Trained with NAI, tested with nutmegmix, lebonmix, and forbiddenmix. The latter act up sometimes but if you want more realism it's the best option.
I did not tested it with realistic models, because NAI based loras never work well on those.

If the girl is not sitting on a face like she should , add : 1girl, 1boy.
